---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Consulting"
  description="Consulting on AI literacy, Human-AI Interaction and psychologically informed AI adoption."
>
  <section class="page-shell">
    <header class="page-header">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Consulting</p>
        <h1>
          Consulting, workshops and talks on AI literacy, Human-AI Interaction and the
          psychology of working with AI.
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p>
        Research-informed support for organizations, teams and institutions that need to
        understand how people actually work, decide, communicate and create with AI.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="two-column">
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Prompted Psyche treats AI adoption as a human and organizational question, not
          only a technical rollout. The work focuses on literacy, trust, judgment,
          communication and the psychological realities of using generative tools.
        </p>
        <p>
          Consulting, workshops and talks can help teams develop clearer language for AI,
          notice risks in everyday use, and build more thoughtful habits around automation,
          authorship, review and responsibility.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h3>Focus areas</h3>
          <ul class="plain-list">
            <li>AI literacy for organizations</li>
            <li>Human-AI Interaction</li>
            <li>Trust and decision-making with AI</li>
            <li>Psychology of working with generative tools</li>
            <li>AI in communication, creativity and culture</li>
            <li>Responsible use of AI in teams and workflows</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="panel">
          <h3>Best fit</h3>
          <ul class="plain-list">
            <li>Organizations starting to structure AI use</li>
            <li>Teams working with content, communication, education or creative workflows</li>
            <li>Leaders who need to understand the human side of AI adoption</li>
            <li>Institutions looking for talks or workshops on AI and cyberpsychology</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="panel">
          <h3>Formats</h3>
          <ul class="plain-list">
            <li>Expert briefing</li>
            <li>Workshop</li>
            <li>Advisory session</li>
            <li>Talk / lecture</li>
            <li>Research-informed content or review</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel page-note">
      <h2>Research-informed note</h2>
      <p>
        This work is informed by ongoing research, source-based writing and registered
        research projects in progress. It does not replace legal, clinical or compliance
        advice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
